---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---
<BaseLayout title="BridgeAIChat Roadmap" description="BridgeAIChat beta roadmap and near-term product work.">
  <section class="surface">
    <div class="eyebrow">Roadmap</div>
    <h1>What we are tightening after the current beta.</h1>
    <p class="lede">
      The current milestone is runtime reliability: clearer session ownership, better tool switching, and fewer
      confusing setup edges around device status and reconnects.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section-gap grid two">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="eyebrow">Near Term</div>
      <h2>Beta hardening</h2>
      <ul class="list tight">
        <li>Improve explicit tool switching inside a device chat</li>
        <li>Tighten agent-side failure surfacing for auth, quota, and missing tool binaries</li>
        <li>Expand the tested platform matrix and release cadence</li>
        <li>Smooth service installation and post-install checks on agent devices</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="eyebrow">Runtime</div>
      <h2>Execution model improvements</h2>
      <ul class="list tight">
        <li>Safer per-chat Codex session continuation</li>
        <li>Clearer multi-device reconnection handling and visibility</li>
        <li>Better file-transfer and artifact-return workflows</li>
        <li>More predictable conversation persistence across tool adapters</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
